          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1674831624234-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1674831624234-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once lightly caramelised, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> ground coriander </strong>with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and cook for 30 secs</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1674831633801-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
